{
  "stem": "13063.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Jews were also quartered in the-- in the factory, in Schindler's factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So Titsch, knowing, having known Schindler well, interceded on our behalf, on behalf of my father and myself, that we should be included in his list.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew only that those Jews were well provided for by Schindler, who-- those who were, who were working for him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And thank god [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was successful.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were included in the list of Schindler's-- of Schindler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that when the camp was liquidated in September 1944, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we went together with the people of the Emalia office of this factory, with one transport to the main concentration camp of Gross-Rosen in Germany.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were transported in cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Plaszow, I worked at Madritsch, where Titsch, Raimund Titsch was also the-- one of the-- owners, or one of the directors.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was really a director, one of the directors, yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think once or twice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He visited the, the Plaszow camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I saw-- I had, I got a glimpse of him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because they were iso-- they were completely separated from us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There we had-- there is no-- there were-- there was-- the only contact we had with them was through the Polish go, go-betweens, suppliers of raw material.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Possibly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I cannot remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think I knew some of them, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was always torture.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was always torture.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was not only-- chicanery and, and, and torture for torture's sake.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, for example we were-- after we worked a whole day, we were chased out from our barracks and made to carry big stones to one place, and then from that place back and deposit it where they were.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
